{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Review waiting times for diagnosis and treatment of IBD",
        "additional_details": "Here are actionable steps that can be taken:\r\n \r\nEnsure more specialists available in gastro departments to reduce waiting times for initial consultations.\r\n \r\nInvest in the expansion of diagnostic facilities & staff training to expedite procedures eg colonoscopies/imaging.\r\n \r\nIntroduce priority triage system for patients with suspected IBD to ensure fast-tracked diagnostic & treatment processes for most at risk.\r\n \r\nEquip General Practitioners with better resources & training to recognize IBD symptoms early.\r\n",
        "background": "The government should conduct a review with the aim of streamlining the diagnostic and treatment pathways for suspected IBD cases. ",
